expression = re.compile(rfc._PATH_AV_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['Path=', 'Path=\t~some/random/path.foo',
    'path=~some/random/path.foo', 'Path=~some/random/path.foo;']
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad Path AV '{m}' matched by regex".format(m=bad_example))
